<section id="main-content">
  <section class="wrapper">
      <div class="row centered">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <h1>Card Sorting</h1>
		        <h3>Test your users using card sorting.</h3>
            <%= link_to "Start Test", confirm_test_path(:url => current_project.sorting_test.url, :id => current_project.sorting_test.id), :target => "_blank", 'data-no-turbolink' => true, :class => "btn btn-default btn-success"  %>
            <%= link_to("Image Gallery", project_card_images_path, 'data-no-turbolink' => true, :class => "btn btn-default btn-success" )  %>
          </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row centered">
      </div>
      <div class="row">
      	<%= render "form_new_card" %>
      </div>
      <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="row">
          <%= render "list_cards" %>
        </div>
      </div>
  </section>
</section>
<div id="help-sidebar">
  <div>
    <ul>
      <li>Write a card for each site information. Example: about, main content, search form, user friends, user features, login buttons...</li><br />
      <li>Click on "Start test" and a new window will be opened. This window is where the user will make the test.</li><br />
      <li>You can change the color of your cards, it will help you to compare the different tests easly.</li><br />
      <li>Drag and drop the cards, is very easy and intuitive.</li><br />
      <li>After the test, save and download the image. You can download as many images as you can.</li><br />
      <li>In the "Image Gallery" you will be able to upload the tests.</li><br />
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>